---
layout: base.njk
title: Speaking
description: Book Dr. Raj Shah for keynotes and conference presentations on transforming math education
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-12 text-primary">Speaking & Keynotes</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-12">{{ description }}</p>

    {# Introduction Section #}
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
      <div>
        <div class="prose lg:prose-lg">
          <p><strong>I'm on a mission to transform math class in a place where ALL students experience the joy and wonder of mathematics.</strong></p>
          <p>If you are conference organizer or hosting a PD day for K-12 math teachers and you're looking for someone to energize teachers, honor their dedication, and inspire them to get out of their comfort zones, let's talk!</p>
          <p>I help teachers use simple strategies to <strong>spark curiosity</strong>, encourage <strong>productive struggle</strong>, and foster <strong>meaningful discourse</strong> to develop deeper conceptual understanding and promote joy in the mathematics classroom.</p>
          <p>I've had the privilege of speaking and keynoting at international, national, and state conferences, including:</p>
          <ul class="leading-none">
            <li>NCTM 
            <li>The National Math Festival
            <li>CMC-South & CMC-North (California)
            <li>Florida CTM
            <li>Iowa CTM
            <li>Minnesota CTM
            <li>Ohio CTM
            <li>CAMT (Texas)
            <li>and many more!
          </ul>I also deliver professional development and coaching for individual schools and districts throughout the U.S.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
        <img src="/images/CAMT 2.jpg" alt="Dr. Raj Shah speaking at conference" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      </div>
    </div>

    {# Popular Keynotes Section #}
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary text-center">Popular Keynotes</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {% for talk in talks %}
        {% if talk.type == "keynote" %}
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl rounded-2xl">
          <figure class="rounded-t-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/{{ talk.image }}" alt="{{ talk.title }}" class="w-full h-64 object-cover">
          </figure>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">{{ talk.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ talk.description }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
